        "client_msg_id": "dfb5687d-3703-46fe-bba8-914b4d5784bf",
        "text": "<@UC2A2ARPT> your comment radically upends my view of the cosmos (for the better). That level of polish definitely feels more attainable. Now I'm curious what Stefan thinks of it.\n\n<https:\/\/github.com\/cblgh\/cerca|Here's the codebase used for Merveilles forum.>\n\n<https:\/\/forum.merveilles.town\/thread\/86\/%5bmeta%5d-forum-utilisation-27|Here's a recent thread of Merveilles forum trying to decide what they want>. Not directly applicable but might give y'all a sense for its strengths and weaknesses. It's a very different context here, so we could decide very differently on each feature.\n\nBut perhaps it's premature to start thinking in terms of features..",
