                                "type": "link",
                                "url": "https:\/\/forum.merveilles.town\/thread\/86\/%5bmeta%5d-forum-utilisation-27",
                                "text": "Here's a recent thread of Merveilles forum trying to decide what they want"
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": ". Not directly applicable but might give y'all a sense for its strengths and weaknesses. It's a very different context here, so we could decide very differently on each feature.\n\nBut perhaps it's premature to start thinking in terms of features.."
